column1: If set to yes, the "Fill Form" button is only shown in developer mode. The scripts are loaded regardless and can be used on the JavaScript console, for example with <tt>formFiller.fill(billingForm.form)</tt>
column2: If set to yes, the "Fill Form" button is only shown in developer mode. The scripts are loaded regardless and can be used on the JavaScript console, for example with <tt>formFiller.fill(billingForm.form)</tt>
